"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T11:57:44.000Z","msg":"中國四千年黎都係將人肉煮黎放入口既野蠻之地"},{"pid":"4365b05decf1f8eb4065efc9df5ad4236ac564f6","tid":713429,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T07:10:25.000Z","msg":"我迫不及待好想去吃兒了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac01d8e280d6104218a2ef10fde1f73402595234","tid":713429,"uid":128568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T07:58:35.000Z","msg":"人往往憎和尚，憎尼姑，憎回教徒，憎耶教徒，而不憎道士。懂得此理者，懂得中國大半。<br />\n<br />\n魯迅評中國人之確切,一個土生土長既中國人一生都未必悟得到"},{"pid":"f895ed55d3afc077a94477817e2c71a73f26f477","tid":713429,"uid":144626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T08:08:28.000Z","msg":"狂人日記?"},{"pid":"7b1d6f7b59e3c7e0feb433a03757659aebecb4c5","tid":713429,"uid":144626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2e14a241c4a3a06c43a8e1c2a8b3c49658b100ca","tid":713429,"uid":167757,"like":6,"dislike":10,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T06:23:06.000Z","msg":"鲁迅生於現代一定係雙失廢青日日上連登開post"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T08:09:29.000Z","msg":"笑甚麼，畜牲，你也是廢青"},{"pid":"4a3c28ad529f7b16df134acfc41c8542bce69066","tid":713429,"uid":41057,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2e14a241c4a3a06c43a8e1c2a8b3c49658b100ca","tid":713429,"uid":167757,"like":6,"dislike":10,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T06:23:06.000Z","msg":"鲁迅生於現代一定係雙失廢青日日上連登開post"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T08:12:15.000Z","msg":"傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  讀多啲書啦 周樹人以前係醫生  同埋人地係書香世家嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}